WEBVTT

00:07.069 --> 00:08.803
<i>Previously on The Affair...</i>

00:08.805 --> 00:10.738
<i>I'm here
because the library claims</i>

00:10.740 --> 00:12.239
<i>to have
unearthed certain pages from</i>

00:12.241 --> 00:13.773
<i>a rare manuscript that</i>

00:13.775 --> 00:15.441
<i>I happen to be an expert on.</i>

00:15.443 --> 00:17.511
- And do they?
- If I had to wager a guess,

00:17.513 --> 00:19.078
<i>- I'd say no.
- So you have,</i>

00:19.080 --> 00:22.148
some kind of arrangement
with your husband?

00:22.150 --> 00:24.083
My husband suffers from Alzheimer's...

00:27.022 --> 00:29.088
<i>But we don't have
an arrangement, as you say.</i>

00:29.090 --> 00:31.189
<i>Half the time,
he doesn't even remember</i>

00:31.191 --> 00:33.826
<i>he has a wife, or
he thinks I'm his first wife,</i>

00:33.828 --> 00:35.327
<i>whom he loved better.</i>

00:35.329 --> 00:37.095
This has to end right now.

00:37.097 --> 00:39.264
- He's using you.
- You have no fucking idea

00:39.266 --> 00:41.000
- what you're talking about.
- Yes, I do!

00:41.002 --> 00:43.502
How many assistants do you
think he's gone through?

00:43.504 --> 00:44.870
What are you, 50?

00:44.872 --> 00:46.805
Maybe she does have some daddy issues.

00:46.807 --> 00:49.373
You know, tends to happen
when your father's a scumbag.

00:49.375 --> 00:50.875
<i>She tells me
everything, Solloway.</i>

00:50.877 --> 00:53.177
<i>I know it all...
the fucking hot tub.</i>

00:53.179 --> 00:55.613
- Dad, what the fuck?
- Shit.

00:55.615 --> 00:56.681
What the fuck is wrong with you?

00:56.683 --> 00:58.282
- Dad?
- Whitney...

01:01.187 --> 01:03.955
- I know you.
- You don't know me.

01:03.957 --> 01:05.188
Ahhah, no, Noah!

01:05.190 --> 01:08.124
Aahhh.

